text: Liu Zhaowu is an archer from China. He was born on 12 October 1988 in Fujian. Zhaowu competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics.Liu ZhaowuZhaowu LIU == References == Category:Chinese archers Category:Olympians for China Category:People from Fujian Category:1988 births Category:Living people
